Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝在哪?
